summary: Adds a treehouse, which you can use as playerhome !
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a playerhome to the game, which is implemented into Skyrim, so you don\'t have to go through load-doors.

The nice thing about this playerhome (as you can see in the screens): It\'s a treehouse !

I did not put things like mannequins, shrines or an alchemy lab into the home.
You can only find some Barrels/Chest and a cooking-place and of course a place to sleep (look at screens)
author: onur53
